# Glob patterns (relative to NOTES_ROOT) excluded from indexing.
# Whole-vault indexing is the current default (your choice), so employer paths
# stay indexed and are filtered at QUERY time instead (--exclude / search-personal).
# Uncomment below to exclude them from the index entirely (north-star vault split).

.obsidian/*
.trash/*
templates/*

# private/*
# private/work-*
# **/threads/*
# **/*confluence*
